%20in%20the%20team%20but%20also%20in%20the%20PCB.%20According%20to%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20sources%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20before%20Babar%20Azam%20on%20his%20comeback%20as%20captain%20was%20to%20unite%20the%20team%20but%20he%20could%20not%20do%20so%20because%20of%20the%20groupings.%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20upset%20at%20losing%20the%20captaincy%20and%20Babar%20not%20supporting%20him%20when%20required%20while%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20was%20unhappy%20at%20not%20being%20considered%20for%20the%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20three%20groups%20in%20the%20team%2C%20one%20led%20by%20Babar%20Azam%2C%20the%20second%20one%20by%20Shaheen%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20and%20the%20third%20one%20by%20Mohammad%20Rizwan.%20Add%20to%20this%20mix%20the%20return%20of%20seniors%20like%20Mohammad%20Aamir%20and%20Imad%20Wasim%20and%20the%20recipe%20was%20ready%20for%20a%20World%20Cup%20disaster%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20team%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20return%20of%20Imad%20and%20Amir%20added%20to%20the%20confusion%20as%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20Babar%20to%20get%20any%20worthwhile%20performances%20from%20both%20of%20them%20as%20they%20had%20not%20played%20top%20level%20domestic%20or%20international%20cricket%20for%20a%20long%20while%20now%20except%20in%20franchise%20based%20leagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20even%20instances%20where%20some%20players%20were%20not%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20and%20a%20few%20of%20them%20even%20tried%20to%20appease%20all%20the%20group%20leaders%20in%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20PCB%20official%20said%20that%20Chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20team%20even%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20had%20been%20briefed%20by%20his%20right%20hand%2C%20national%20selector%20and%20senior%20manager%2C%20Wahab%20Riaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNaqvi%20held%20two%20meetings%20with%20all%20the%20players%20in%20private%20and%20gave%20them%20pep%20talks%20asking%20them%20to%20put%20their%20issues%20aside%20and%20focus%20on%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20he%20would%20remove%20all%20misgivings%20in%20the%20team%20later%20on%20but%20apparently%20things%20didn't%20work%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20defending%20Babar%20but%20what%20is%20a%20captain%20supposed%20to%20do%20when%20your%20premier%20bowler%20can't%20even%20defend%2015%20in%20the%20final%20over%20against%20a%20weak%20USA%20side%20and%20concedes%20a%20boundary%20and%20six%20on%20full%20tosses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOr%20when%20an%20all-rounder%20brought%20out%20of%20retirement%20to%20help%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20sits%20out%20with%20fitness%20issues.%26quot%3B%20The%20role%20of%20outside%20elements%20including%20agents%20of%20players%20and%20some%20former%20players%20who%20ran%20social%20media%20campaigns%20also%20have%20not%20helped%20ease%20the%20simmering%20tensions%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20has%20now%20hinted%20at%20making%20changes%20in%20the%20national%20team%20but%20another%20well-informed%20source%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20changes%20would%20now%20also%20be%20made%20in%20the%20cricket%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chairman%20obviously%20is%20going%20to%20clean%20up%20things%20in%20the%20team%20but%20already%20he%20has%20started%20a%20process%20of%20performance%20related%20appraisals%20of%20senior%20and%20mid%20level%20employees%20in%20the%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20see%20major%20changes%20in%20the%20team%20and%20at%20management%20level%20in%20the%20board%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNaqvi%20is%20himself%20facing%20problems%20as%20he%20is%20not%20the%20ruling%20government's%20choice%20to%20head%20the%20board.%20He%20is%20also%20now%20facing%20criticism%20for%20the%20WC%20debacle%20and%20there%20are%20calls%20for%20his%20head%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20PCB%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20reliable%20sources%20have%20also%20confirmed%20that%20Naqvi%20will%20not%20be%20making%20an%20immediate%20call%20on%20Babar%20Azam's%20captaincy%20since%20Pakistan%20now%20plays%20its%20next%20white%20ball%20series%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20good%20thing%20for%20Naqvi%20is%20that%20Pakistan%20now%20has%20two%20test%20series%20lined%20up%20at%20home%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20England%20and%20with%20Shan%20Masood%20already%20the%20test%20captain%20and%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20in%20Jason%20Gillispie%20and%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20immediate%20changes.%E2%80%9D%20Usually%20in%20Pakistan%20cricket%20a%20failed%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20means%20that%20heads%20roll%20and%20the%20board%20tends%20to%20search%20for%20scapegoats%20but%20this%20time%20even%20the%20cricket%20fans%20and%20critics%20are%20pushing%20the%20PCB%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20stop%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718448600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fcv8ebqao_pakistan-grouping_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-were-pakistan-knocked-out-of-t20-world-cup-3-groups-in-team-mohammad-rizwan-not-happy-5895434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20came%20to%20a%20disastrous%20end%20as%20the%20team%20failed%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20group%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-were-pakistan-knocked-out-of-t20-world-cup-3-groups-in-team-mohammad-rizwan-not-happy-5895434%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-