gland%20medical%20director%20Stephen%20Powis%20said%20such%20drugs%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20with%20proper%20medical%20supervision%20and%20warned%20that%20they%20could%20have%20potentially%20dangerous%20side%20effects%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Fuk%2Fhealthcare%2Farticle%2Fyoung-women-buying-ozempic-beach-body-ready-end-up-a-and-e-9rjjrpghn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20NHS%20Confederation%20conference%2C%20Powis%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20these%20new%20drugs%20will%20be%20a%20powerful%20part%20of%20our%20arsenal%20dealing%20with%20obesity%2C%20but%20they%20should%20not%20be%20abused.%20Buying%20medication%20online%20without%20a%20doctor's%20supervision%20can%20lead%20to%20complications%20and%20dangerous%20consequences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrugs%20including%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20should%20only%20be%20used%20by%20people%20prescribed%20them%20for%20obesity%20or%20diabetes.%20I'm%20worried%20about%20reports%20that%20people%20are%20misusing%20them%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20not%20intended%20as%20a%20quick%20fix%20for%20people%20trying%20to%20get%20'beach%20body%20ready.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVicky%20Price%2C%20an%20acute%20physician%20and%20president-elect%20of%20the%20Society%20for%20Acute%20Medicine%2C%20said%20some%20of%20the%20more%20dangerous%20potential%20side%20effects%20of%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20bought%20online%20included%20%26quot%3Bserious%2C%20life-threatening%20complications%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Binflammation%20of%20the%20pancreas%20gland%20and%20alterations%20in%20blood%20salt%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20such%20as%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20have%20soared%20in%20popularity%20over%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boom%20in%20Ozempic%20sales%20has%20even%20helped%20its%20maker%2C%20Danish%20company%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20become%20%