i%3EWriter%20Sarah%20Wood%20breaks%20down%20the%20logistics%20and%20drivers%20of%20phone-free%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESix%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20spent%20ten%20days%20without%20my%20phone%20at%20a%20meditation%20retreat%20in%20Thailand.%20The%20experience%20was%20so%20refreshing%20that%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20a%20new%20brain.%20I%20vowed%20to%20use%20my%20phone%20less%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20habit%20didn't%20stick.%20My%20phone%20usage%20has%20skyrocketed%20in%20the%20years%20since%2C%20sometimes%20clocking%20ten%20hours%20of%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlanning%20a%20wedding%20and%20buying%20an%20apartment%20in%20the%20same%20month%20brought%20my%20digital%20dependence%20to%20new%20heights.%20On%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkilliehuntly.scot%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EScottish%20cabin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20advertised%20as%20somewhere%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20where%20the%20world%20can't%20find%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20tried%20to%20go%20tech-free%20and%20reset.%20With%20an%20itinerary%20of%20fly%20fishing%20and%20hiking%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20unplug.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20wrong.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20days%20were%20fine%2C%20but%20right%20before%20bed%2C%20I%20couldn't%20stop%20myself%20from%20scrolling%20through%20my%20email%20and%20notifications.%20I%20felt%20disheartened%20by%20my%20failed%20attempt%20to%20unplug.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4856187-6b2c-4308-bb8b-c3861f3e350d%5C%22%3E62%25%20of%20adults%20aged%2018%20to%2029%20say%20they're%20constantly%20online%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20unable%20to%20put%20your%20phone%20down%2C%20even%20on%20vacation%2C%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20common.%20In%202024%2C%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20surveyed%20nearly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Famericans-use-of-mobile-technology-and-home-broadband%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E6%2C000%20US%20adults%20on%20their%20tech%20usage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%2062%25%20of%20participants%20between%2018%20and%2029%20said%20they%20are%20almost%20constantly%20online.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20this%20constant%20online-ness%2C%20people%20also%20want%20to%20disconnect%20completely%2C%20especially%20while%20on%20vacation.%20Global%20search%20interest%20for%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20detox%20retreat%26quot%3B%20has%20increased%20by%2050%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20No%20longer%20beholden%20to%20emails%20and%20Slacks%2C%20vacations%20are%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20shut%20down%20devices%2C%20and%20people%20are%20turning%20to%20the%20tourism%20industry%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22324f24ff-6611-474d-9e8b-387488fb6692%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20are%20turning%20to%20the%20tourism%20industry%20to%20help%20them%20unplug%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProperty%20managers%20and%20tour%20operators%20are%20offering%20unplugged%20trips%20and%20tech-free%20destinations%20to%20meet%20this%20demand.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funplugged.rest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnplugged%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20cabin%20company%20in%20the%20UK%20offering%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20detox%26quot%3B%20long%20weekends%20in%20nature.%20Guests%20can%20use%20their%20phones%20to%20navigate%20to%20their%20Unplugged%20cabins%2C%20but%20once%20they%20arrive%2C%20they're%20expected%20to%20lock%20their%20phones%20in%20a%20box%20for%20their%20trip.%20The%20cabins%20have%20a%20paper%20map%2C%20a%20Polaroid%20camera%20for%20travelers%2C%20and%20a%20retro%20Nokia%20phone%20for%20emergencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20we%20found%20is%20to%20give%20people%20all%20the%20things%20that%20they%20might%20need%20their%20phone%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hector%20Hughes%2C%20CEO%20of%20Unplugged.%20The%20company%20launched%20in%202020%20and%20has%2023%20cabins%20and%20a%2094%25%20occupancy%20rate%20since%20July%20last%20year%2C%20marking%20a%20209%25%20increase%20in%20bookings%20over%20the%20previous%2012%20months%2C%20according%20to%20Hughes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGroup%20travel%20operator%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftlotravel.com%2Fphone-free-trips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20The%20Love%20of%20Travel%20(FTLO)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ran%20its%20first%20phone-free%20trip%20this%20February%20and%20a%20second%20in%20April%2C%20and%20five%20more%20are%20listed%20on%20its%20site%20through%202025.%20For%20FTLO%2C%20the%20trips%20become%20%26quot%3Bphone-free%26quot%3B%20once%20you%20arrive%20at%20the%20first%20hotel%20and%20meet%20your%20tour%20operator%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20logistics%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFTLO%20CEO%20Tara%20Cappel%20said%20guests%20are%20asked%20to%20leave%20their%20phones%20in%20their%20hotel%20safe%20or%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20their%20bags%20when%20the%20group%20is%20together.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20also%20obviously%20not%20controlling%20whether%20people%20are%20going%20back%20to%20the%20rooms%20and%20getting%20on%20their%20phones.%20It's%20an%20honor%20policy.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Cappel%2C%20their%20first%20two%20trips%20were%20filled%2C%20and%20all%20guests%20expressed%20interest%20in%20another%20%26quot%3Bphone-free%26quot%3B%20trip.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20acknowledged%20that%20tech-free%20travel%20hasn't%20become%20completely%20mainstream%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20still%20a%20little%20intimidated%20by%20the%20idea.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHughes%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20haven't%20switched%20their%20phones%20off%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Hughes%20added.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20experience%20phantom%20buzzes%20and%20find%20themselves%20searching%20for%20their%20phone%20instinctively%20before%20remembering%20it's%20locked%20in%20a%20box.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3abbc45-e1fb-489d-879d-2b2b74fd172d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reasons%20for%20going%20phone-free%20when%20traveling%20vary%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20popular%20motivation%20is%20for%20couples%20to%20spend%20quality%20time%20with%20their%20partners.%20Hughes%20told%20BI%20that%2080%25%20of%20their%20guests%20are%20couples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElena%20Mnayarji%2C%20an%20MBA%20student%20at%20Berkeley%2C%20went%20on%20a%20phone-free%20honeymoon%20with%20her%20husband%20in%20Mallorca%20last%20summer.%20She%20said%20she%20didn't%20plan%20it%20but%20wanted%20to%20disconnect%20after%20a%20busy%20wedding.%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20Mallorca%2C%20I%20was%20exhausted%20and%20really%20needed%20to%20shut%20my%20brain%20off.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20she%20arrived%20in%20Mallorca%2C%20she%20turned%20her%20phone%20off%20and%20put%20it%20in%20a%20drawer%20at%20their%20hotel%20for%20their%20entire%20trip.%20Not%20checking%20her%20phone%20was%20difficult%2C%20but%20Elena%20was%20happy%20that%20she%20committed%20to%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20couple%20hours%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20felt%20a%20lot%20less%20anxious.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20said%20her%20husband%20felt%20more%20connected%20to%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c543866-3955-403b-83c8-e9ddc90b224c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPhone-free%20travel%20can%20also%20help%20with%20burnout%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20summer%2C%20nonprofit%20strategist%20Izzy%20Doonan%20did%20a%20tech-free%20week-long%20trip%20in%20the%20Cascades%20with%20her%20partner%20and%20another%20couple.%20They%20wouldn't%20have%20cell%20service%2C%20so%20they%20embraced%20the%20opportunity%20to%20get%20offline.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20trip%20got%20closer%2C%20we%20all%20realized%20how%20burnt%20out%20we%20were.%20It%20was%20fitting%20to%20take%20a%20trip%20without%20our%20phones%20and%20really%20unplug%2C%26quot%3B%20Doonan%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20they%20drove%20into%20the%20park%20and%20lost%20service%2C%20the%20group%20put%20their%20phones%20in%20the%20glove%20compartment%20of%20their%20car%20and%20didn't%20use%20them%20until%20they%20left%20the%20park.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20nerves%20were%20from%20our%20parents%20because%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20contact%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doonan%2C%20who%20wasn't%20personally%20concerned.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20quite%20safe%20in%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20national%20park%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20had%20a%20car%20and%20other%20campers%20were%20around.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%201%2C000%25%20do%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4175990-8683-44be-94c9-7291952c55c5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ELogistics%20of%20traveling%20phone-free%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETraveling%20phone-free%20does%20pose%20some%20logistical%20issues.%20%26quot%3BOne%20concern%20that%20was%20brought%20up%20was%20that%20people's%20families%20back%20home%20were%20worried%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cappel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFTLO%20provides%20the%20trip%20leaders'%20phone%20numbers%20and%20full%20itineraries%20with%20contact%20information%20to%20travelers%20to%20share%20with%20whoever%20might%20need%20it.%20Mnayarji%20echoed%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20recommend%20people%20tell%20their%20family%20if%20they're%20going%20to%20go%20phone-free.%20My%20mom%20was%20freaking%20out%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20text%20her%20from%20my%20husband's%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20both%20FTLO%20and%20Unplugged%2C%20you%20can%20use%20your%20phone%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20to%20the%20destination%20and%20then%20are%20asked%20to%20put%20your%20phone%20away.%20Traveling%20domestically%2C%20bringing%20an%20emergency%20prepaid%20phone%2C%20or%20traveling%20with%20a%20tour%20operator%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20logistics%20are%20ways%20to%20make%20your%20tech-free%20trip%20as%20safe%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECappel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCommitting%20to%20a%20multi-day%20phone-free%20trip%20is%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20if%20people%20can%20start%20with%20an%20afternoon%20and%20leave%20their%20phone%20in%20their%20hotel%20for%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20start%20and%20realize%20it's%20really%20doable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphone-free-vacations-digital-detox-summer-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718447401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c431ded9a404d829dbfa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphone-free-vacations-digital-detox-summer-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overstimulated%20workers%20are%20turning%20to%20the%20tourism%20industry%20to%20help%20them%20break%20their%20screen%20addiction%20and%20switch%20off%20on%20vacation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Wood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphone-free-vacations-digital-detox-summer-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20one%2