g%20from%20zip%20codes%20across%20Africa%2C%20Asia%2C%20Central%20America%2C%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20downtown%20Celina%2C%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661fba0d0b8e1c832ccafd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221327%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDowntown%20Celina%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Celina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20has%20surged%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20domestic%20migration%20within%20the%20United%20States.%20While%20major%20cities%20like%20Austin%2C%20Dallas%2C%20and%20Houston%20have%20long%20spearheaded%20the%20state's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-texas-from-california-florida-ny-generations-income-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520average%2520yearly%2520income%2520of%2Cnot%2520in%2520the%2520labor%2520force.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edramatic%20population%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20smaller%2C%20lesser-known%20areas%20such%20as%20Celina%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-new-braunfels-texas-real-estate-jobs-schlitterbahn-wurstfest-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Braunfels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-texas-surprised-at-what-cities-they-are-choosing-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaty%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20now%20taking%20the%20lead.%20Their%20rising%20popularity%20is%20partly%20attributed%20to%20what%20they%20offer%20that%20many%20bigger%20cities%20can't%3A%20a%20down-to-earth%20lifestyle%2C%20relatively%20low%20costs%2C%20and%20homes%20ripe%20for%20the%20picking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20growing%20at%20about%2020%25%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Tubbs%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Celina%20since%20May%202023%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20astron