ust%2520a%2520week%2520before%2Cthree%2520lanes%2520in%2520each%2520direction.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorth%20Texas%20Tollway%20Authority%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20plans%20to%20extend%20further%20into%20Prosper%20and%20Celina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20sign%2C%20positioned%20near%20the%20town's%20entrance%2C%20showcases%20the%20array%20of%20homebuilders%20in%20Celina%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661f32ecc442a2f676eb5df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20sign%2C%20positioned%20near%20the%20town's%20entrance%2C%20showcases%20the%20array%20of%20homebuilders%20in%20Celina%3Cp%3EAlcynna%20Lloyd%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Celina%20becoming%20more%20accessible%2C%20numerous%20new%20housing%20developments%20led%20by%20builders%20like%20Taylor%20Morrison%2C%20Toll%20Brothers%2C%20and%20Highland%20Homes%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20have%20heightened%20the%20area's%20appeal%20for%20both%20local%20Texans%20and%20transplant%20renters%20and%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20city%2C%20from%202010%20until%20June%202024%2C%2015%2C062%20single-family%20permits%20have%20been%20issued%20for%20Celina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20new%20homes%20in%20Celina%20have%20been%20built%20north%20of%20the%20downtown%20area%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20border%20with%20Prosper%2C%26quot%3B%20Tubbs%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221890%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20overview%20of%20the%20Mustang%20Lakes%20neighborhood%20by%20Highland%20Homes%20in%20Celina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661f509d0b8e1c832ccaace%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221259%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mustang%20Lakes%20neighborhood%20by%20Highland%20Homes%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20developments%20in%20Celina%20by%20this%20homebuilder%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Highland%20Homes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHomebuyers%20have%20been%20drawn%20in%20by%20Celina's%20charming%20small-town%20vibe%20and%20its%20array%20of%20expansive%2C%20modern%20homes%20within%20meticulously%20master-planned%20communities.%20These%20tailor-made%20residential%20neighborhoods%2C%20often%20built%20on%20more%20than%202%2C500%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20functioning%20like%20mini-cities%2C%20can%20vary%20in%20size%20from%20100%20to%2050%2C000%20homes%2C%20as%20noted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankrate.com%2Freal-estate%2Fwhat-is-a-master-planned-community%2F%23charac%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBankrate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Celina's%20Highland%20Homes'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmustanglakes.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustang%20Lakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20neighborhood%2C%20residents%20are%20treated%20to%20an%20extensive%20list%20of%20amenities%2C%20including%20a%2012%2C000-square-foot%20private%20amenity%20center%2C%20junior%20Olympic%20and%20resort-style%20pools%2C%20a%20fitness%20center%2C%20four%20competition%20tennis%20courts%2C%20an%20amphitheater%2C%2018%20miles%20of%20trails%2C%20playgrounds%2C%20an%20event%20lawn%2C%20as%20well%20as%2014%20lakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20community%20is%20not%20an%20exception%20in%20Celina%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20become%20the%20standard%20for%20homebuilders%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20communities%20are%20all-encompassing%2C%26quot%3B%20Julissa%20Casas%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20at%20the%20JC%20Porcher%20Real%20Estate%20Group%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20attractions%20and%20something%20for%20everybody.%20You%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20go%20further%20out%20of%20the%20community%2C%20I%20think%20that%20is%20appealing%20to%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20city's%20real%20estate%20market%20is%20booming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Graham%2C%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.highlandhomes.com%2Fdfw%2Fcelina%2F%23minPrice%3D490000%26amp%3BmaxPrice%3D2260000%26amp%3BmaxSqFootage%3D6200%26amp%3BminSqFootage%3D1600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHighland%20Homes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20back%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20the%20company%20began%20building%20in%20Celina%2C%20but%20the%20timing%20was%20premature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20completely%20flipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20knew%20Celina%20had%20the%20potential%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20build%20homes%20where%20the%20market%20wants%20to%20buy%20and%20in%202004%20it%20was%20too%20far%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Graham%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20population%20growth%20has%20been%20astounding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHighland%20Homes%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20luxury%20homes%20within%20master-planned%20communities%2C%20has%20built%20several%20successful%20neighborhoods%20in%20Celina%20since%202020%20including%20Mustang%20Lakes%2C%20The%20Parks%20at%20Wilson%20Creek%2C%20Cambridge%20Crossing%2C%20and%20the%20Mosaic.%20Home%20prices%20in%20these%20neighborhoods%20start%20in%20the%20low%20%24500%2C000s%20and%20reach%20into%20the%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%20said%20that%20to%20date%2C%20Highland%20Homes%20has%20closed%201%2C930%20home%20sales%20in%20Celina%2C%20and%20by%20year's%20end%2C%20the%20total%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20closer%20to%202%2C100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221417%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20model%20home%20within%20the%20Mustang%20Lakes%20neighborhood%20by%20Highland%20Homes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661f7781cd3b17790440533%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22926%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20model%20home%20within%20the%20Mustang%20Lakes%20neighborhood%20by%20Highland%20Homes.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Highland%20Homes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20abundance%20of%20relatively%20affordable%20homes%20in%20Celina%20has%20attracted%20numerous%20homebuyers%20from%20both%20the%20more%20costly%20West%20and%20East%20Coasts%2C%20according%20to%20Casas%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Celina%20from%20nearby%20Little%20Elm%20six%20years%20ago%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20coming%20from%20other%20states%20like%20California%20and%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%20Casas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20looking%20for%20small-town%20conservative%20areas.%26quot%3B%20Movers%20are%20also%20seeking%20smaller%20communities%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20events%2C%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20Cajun%20fest%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftroubadourfestival.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETroubadour%20Festival%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20Cajun%20Fest%20is%20among%20Texas'%20largest%20crawfish%20boils%2C%20featuring%20live%20music%2C%20vendors%2C%20and%20carnival%20rides.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Troubadour%20is%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20premier%20barbecue%20and%20country%20music%20festivals.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20also%20talking%20about%20putting%20in%20a%20rodeo.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENew%20businesses%20are%20moving%20into%20the%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20people%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Celina's%20economy%20is%20also%20growing%20as%20local%20businesses%20and%20services%20benefit%20from%20increased%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETracy%20Miller%2C%20owner%20of%20downtown%20Celina's%20decor%20boutique%20shop%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fterramaniashop.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETerramania%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20sales%20have%20steadily%20increased%20over%20the%20two%20years%20since%20its%20opening%2C%20and%20she%20anticipates%20this%20trend%20to%20persist%20in%20the%20years%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20coming%20to%20see%20what's%20happening%20in%20this%20town%2C%20so%20our%20customer%20base%20is%20not%20just%20limited%20to%20Celina%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20that%20point%20where%20we're%20waiting%20for%20an%20explosion%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223635%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tracy%20Miller%2C%20owner%20of%20downtown%20Celina's%20decor%20boutique%20shop%2C%20Terramania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661fa981cd3b177904408a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETracy%20Miller%2C%20owner%20of%20downtown%20Celina's%20decor%20boutique%20shop%2C%20Terramania.%3Cp%3EAlcynna%20Lloyd%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETubbs%20said%20the%20city%20is%20constructing%20a%20new%20city%20hall%20and%20expanding%20its%20staff%20to%20accommodate%20its%20growing%20number%20of%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20Celina%20is%20adding%20approximately%2040%20to%2060%20staff%20members%20per%20year%2C%20mainly%20first%20responders%2C%20which%20brings%20the%20total%20number%20of%20city%20employees%20to%20around%20350%20so%20far%20%E2%80%94%20much%20smaller%20than%20Dallas%2C%20which%20had%20about%2015%2C300%20employees%20as%20of%202022%2C%20according%20to%20its%20city%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20pride%20ourselves%20on%20public%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Tubbs%20said.%20%26quot%3BBetween%20public%20works%2C%20fire%2C%20and%20police%2C%20these%20departments%20account%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20our%20new%20hires%20among%20city%20staff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20city%20is%20changing%20but%20is%20holding%20onto%20its%20values%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20influx%20of%20new%20residents%20from%20higher%20cost-of-living%20states%20like%20California%2C%20combined%20with%20Celina's%20notably%20higher%20median%20household%20income%20%E2%80%94%20%2