a%20club%20offering%20all%20age%20ranges%20and%20lifestyles%2C%20from%20social%20to%20golf.%20It's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20kick%20off%20in%20a%20town%20that%20is%20just%20beginning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20downtown%20square%20of%20Celina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661fc5fd0b8e1c832ccb118%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20downtown%20square%20of%20Celina.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Celina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20ongoing%20changes%20in%20Celina%2C%20the%20community%20spirit%20remains%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20became%20particularly%20evident%20following%20rainstorms%20that%20began%20in%20April%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcdfw.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fdallas-county-federal-disaster-declaration-fema-recovery-centers%2F3560344%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520noted%2520in%2520the%2520announcement%2CPolk%252C%2520San%2520Jacinto%252C%2520Trinity%252C%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20disaster%20declaration%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%20for%20several%20counties%2C%20including%20Dallas%20and%20Collin%20County%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Celina%2C%20directly%20in%20the%20path%20of%20a%20tornado%2C%20saw%20six%20homes%20destroyed%20beyond%20repair%20and%20widespread%20damage%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20WFAA%20news%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20residents%20united%20across%20the%20city%2C%20forming%20volunteer%20groups%20and%20providing%20prayers%20and%20mutual%20support.%20Many%20pitched%20in%20by%20clearing%20debris%20from%20homes%2C%20offering%20shelter%2C%20and%20even%20assisting%20with%20tasks%20like%20picking%20up%20diapers%20or%20pet%20food%20for%20those%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20official%20count%20on%20the%20number%20of%20residents%20who%20took%20part%20in%20volunteer%20efforts.%