es%20call%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcourtesy%20meet%26quot%3B%20as%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20is%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20constituency%20for%20a%20RSS%20event%2C%20is%20to%20take%20place%20either%20between%202%20and%204%20pm%20or%20after%20the%20latter's%20visit%20to%20the%20Gorakhnath%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20of%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20meeting%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20are%20significant%20after%20the%20former's%20speech%20this%20week%20in%20Nagpur%3B%20Mr%20Bhagwat's%20speech%20was%20peppered%20with%20criticism%20about%20the%20way%20the%20campaign%20was%20conducted%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20RSS%20chief's%20comment%20was%20veiled%2C%20his%20colleague%20Indresh%20Kumar's%20was%20not%3B%20he%20slammed%20the%20%26quot%3Bparty%20which%20did%20bhakti%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20(a%20reference%20to%20building%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20UP's%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20seal%20a%20landslide%20win%20for%20the%20party)%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20however%2C%20dispelled%20talk%20of%20a%20split%20with%20its%20political%20unit%3B%20sources%20said%20the%20message%20was%20just%20a%20pick-me-up%20for%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20for%20Indresh%20Kumar's%20jab%2C%20RSS%20sources%20distanced%20the%20organisation%20from%20the%20comments%20and%20sought%20to%20flip%20it%2C%20declaring%20Lord%20Ram%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20those%20(the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc)%20who%20became%20arrogant%26quot%3B%20at%20241.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20the%20BJP%20had%20set%20itself%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20370%20seats%20(400%2B%20with%20allies)%20to%20form%20a%20third%20consecutive%20union%20government%20with%20a%20brute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20hobbled%20by%20a%20strong%20showing%20by%20the%20INDIA%20group%2C%20and%20pushback%20over%20policy%20issues%2C%20the%20party's%