5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111017945.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOrry%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Orhan%20Awatramani%2C%20was%20seen%20dining%20with%20reality%20TV%20personality%20Uorfi%20Javed%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20creating%20a%20buzz%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Victim%20In%20Darshan%20Case%20Was%20Not%20Kidnapped%2C%20Says%20Driver%20Who%20Transported%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERavi%2C%20the%20driver%20involved%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20in%20which%20popular%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20are%20accused%2C%20told%20police%20that%20he%20was%20instructed%20to%20take%20the%20fall%20for%20the%20murder%20but%20refused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ravi%2C%20Renuka%20Swamy%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20discovered%20later%2C%20did%20not%20anticipate%20the%20assault%20that%20awaited%20him%20when%20he%20got%20into%20his%20cab.%20Ravi%20stated%20that%20Mr%20Swamy%20was%20not%20forcibly%20taken%20but%20was%20persuaded%20by%20others%20to%20join%20them.%20In%20the%20cab%2C%20the%20others%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20assured%20Mr%20Swamy%20they%20would%20take%20him%20to%20meet%20Darshan%20and%20suggested%20that%20he%20apologise%20for%20his%20social%20media%20comments%20against%20the%20actor's%20girlfriend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20along%20with%20his%20co-star%20and%20girlfriend%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20and%2011%20others%2C%20is%20in%20police%20custody.%20Ms%20Gowda%20allegedly%20prompted%20Darshan%20to%20punish%20Renuka%20Swamy%20for%20derogatory%20remarks%20allegedly%20made%20on%20her%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20transported%20Renuka%20Swamy%20from%20Chitradurga%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20journey%20of%20approximately%20200%20kilometres.%20Upon%20reaching%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ravi%20went%20into%20hiding%20but%20later%20contacted%20the%20taxi%20association%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20who%20advised%20him%20to%20surrender%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi's%20surrender%20on%20Thursday%20night%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police's%20office%20in%20Chitradurga%20has%20given%20a%20new%20direction%20to%20the%20investigation.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Raghu%20alias%20Raghavendra%2C%20who%20managed%20a%20fan%20club%20for%20Darshan%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20arranged%20the%20taxi%20that%20Ravi%20drove.%20Raghu%2C%20along%20with%20others%2C%20had%20organised%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20Renuka%20Swamy%20on%20June%208%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20sequence%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20from%20the%20investigation%20reveal%20that%20Darshan%20and%20his%20aides%20took%20Swamy%20to%20a%20shed%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Kamakshipalya.%20There%2C%20Darshan%20allegedly%20thrashed%20Swamy%20with%20a%20belt%2C%20and%20his%20aides%20beat%20him%20with%20sticks%20until%20he%20lost%20consciousness.%20The%20assault%20resulted%20in%20multiple%20fractures%20and%20severe%20injuries.%20Renuka%20Swamy's%20body%2C%20later%20found%20by%20a%20food%20delivery%20rider%2C%20was%20being%20nibbled%20by%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%20report%20confirmed%20the%20brutal%20nature%20of%20the%20murder%2C%20citing%20shock%20and%20haemorrhage%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20death.%20The%20report%20identified%2015%20wounds%20on%20Swamy's%20body%2C%20with%20injuries%20to%20the%20head%2C%20abdomen%2C%20chest%2C%20and%20other%20parts.%20His%20head%20had%20also%20rammed%20into%20a%20mini-truck%20parked%20at%20the%20shed%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20fatal%20injuries.%20The%20police%20seized%20the%20truck%20and%20other%20instruments%20used%20in%20the%20torture%2C%20including%20wooden%20logs%2C%20a%20leather%20belt%2C%20and%20a%20rope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20allegedly%20planted%20three%20men%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20offering%20them%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20has%20refuted%20allegations%20of%20preferential%20treatment%20being%20given%20to%20Darshan%20during%20his%20detention%20at%20the%20Annapoorneshwari%20Nagar%20police%20station.%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said%20that%20Darshan%20is%20receiving%20the%20same%20treatment%20as%20any%20other%20accused%2C%20dispelling%20rumors%20of%20special%20facilities%20such%20as%20being%20served%20'Biryani'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20police%20to%20give%20Biryani%20and%20royal%20treatment%20to%20the%20accused.%20It%20is%20not%20done%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20also%20denied%20any%20undue%20influence%20over%20the%20investigation.%20Reports%20suggesting%20that%20a%20state%20minister%20was%20attempting%20to%20protect%20Darshan%20were%20strongly%20denied%20by%20Mr%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20said%20no%20political%20pressure%20was%20being%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20pressure%20from%20anyone.....neither%20our%20Home%20Minister%20or%20anyone%20else%20is%20involved%20in%20it%2C%20we%20are%20not%20recommending%20anything%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20across%20Karnataka.%20In%20Kalaburagi%2C%20the%20Jangam%20Samaj%20organised%20a%20massive%20demonstration%20demanding%20severe%20punishment%20for%20Darshan%20and%20his%20associates.%20Protesters%20marched%20from%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20Circle%20to%20the%20District%20Deputy%20Commissioner's%20Office%2C%20where%20they%20burned%20Darshan's%20portrait%20to%20condemn%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20CP%20Yogeshwar%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20former%20MP%20DK%20Suresh%2C%20had%20plans%20to%20field%20Darshan%20as%20a%20Congress%20candidate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Channapatna%20Assembly%20by-election.%20This%20by-election%20is%20pending%20following%20the%20election%20of%20JD(S)%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718442300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F2igkuj6o_darshan-driver-_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-driver-was-asked-to-take-blame-for-murder-in-actor-darshan-case-5894794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravi%2C%20the%20driver%20involved%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20in%20which%20popular%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20are%20accused%2C%20told%20police%20that%20he%20was%20instructed%20to%20take%20the%20fall%20for%20the%20murder%20but%20refused.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-driver-was-asked-to-take-blame-for-murder-in-actor-darshan-case-5894794%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muslim%20pilgrims%20pray%20on%20Mount%20Arafat%20in%20hajj%20climax%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718442171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111018300%2Cimgsize-1067688.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fmuslim-pilgrims-pray-on-mount-arafat-in-hajj-climax%2Farticleshow%2F111017798.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111017798.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMore%20than%201.5%20million%20Muslims%20braved%20extreme%20heat%20to%20reach%20Mount%20Arafat%20on%20Satur