%20runs%20in%20T20%20internationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant%20(Wicketkeeper)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant's%20return%20from%20injury%20has%20been%20promising%20since%20IPL%202024%2C%20and%20his%20aggressive%20batting%20and%20wicket-keeping%20ability%20make%20him%20India's%20first-choice%20gloveman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20has%20scored%201083%20runs%20in%2069%20T20Is%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20126.37%20since%20his%20debut.%20With%2096%20runs%20in%20three%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2048%2C%20the%20southpaw%20is%20currently%20the%20top%20scorer%20for%20India%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20No.1%20T20I%20batter%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20is%20a%20vital%20cog%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad.%20His%20unorthodox%20approach%20with%20the%20bat%20at%20No.4%20provides%20both%20aggression%20and%20guile%20to%20India's%20middle%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKY's%20crucial%20fifty%20against%20the%20USA%20brought%20some%20confidence%20back%20into%20the%20Indian%20camp%20as%20they%20went%20on%20to%20comfortably%20win%20the%20game.%20Indian%20fans%20will%20hope%20the%20swashbuckling%20batter%20will%20be%20at%20his%20best%20against%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivam%20Dube%20had%20a%20great%20IPL%202024%20having%20scored%20396%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20162.30%20for%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%20His%20power-hitting%20and%20handy%20medium%20pace%20brings%20versatility%20and%20options%20to%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20slow%20start%20to%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20his%20crucial%2031-run%20cameo%20against%20the%20USA%20helped%20the%20southpaw%20find%20some%20form%20ahead%20of%20the%20Super%208%20fixtures%20and%20he%20will%20be%20raring%20to%20continue%20his%20momentum%20against%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20had%20a%20mixed%20IPL%20season%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20He%20wasn't%20particularly%20good%20with%20the%20bat%20but%20did%20take%2011%20wickets.%20However%2C%20his%20role%20as%20a%20finisher%20and%20medium-fast%20bowler%20provides%20balance%20to%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-rounder%20has%20taken%20seven%20wickets%20in%20three%20innings%20at%20an%20economy%20of%205.41%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20wicket-takers%20for%20India%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Even%20though%20he's%20yet%20to%20produce%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20hand%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%2C%20he%20plays%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20team%20as%20it%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20we%20see%20him%20at%20his%20free%20flowing%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja's%20all-round%20capabilities%20provide%20depth%20to%20India's%20starting%20XI%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20However%2C%20the%20star%20all-rounder%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20live%20up%20to%20expectations%20in%20the%20three%20league%20matches%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southpaw%20got%20out%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20only%20instance%20he%20got%20to%20bat%20in%20this%20tournament.%20With%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20for%20him%20as%20a%20lower-order%20batter%2C%20Jadeja%20will%20be%20eyeing%20some%20runs%20ahead%20of%20the%20Super%208%20matches%20to%20secure%20his%20place%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3Cbr%3E%5CnLeft-arm%20Chinaman%20bowler%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20had%20a%20wonderful%20IPL%202024%20campaign%20before%20heading%20into%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20The%20leg%20spinner%20took%2016%20wickets%20in%2011%20matches%20at%20an%20economy%20of%208.69%20and%20an%20average%20of%2023.38%20for%20Delhi%20Capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20has%20taken%2059%20T20I%20wickets%20in%2035%20matches%20for%20India%20and%20is%20a%20go-to%20spinner%20in%20white-ball%20formats%20on%20his%20day.%20With%20the%20Super%208%20fixtures%20scheduled%20to%20be%20played%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20India%20might%20include%20the%20star%20spinner%20in%20their%20playing%20XI%20against%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20excellent%20economy%20rate%20of%204.09%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20taken%20five%20wickets%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20and%20is%20currently%20leading%20India's%20bowling%20unit%20in%20style%20having%20won%20two%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20awards%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lethal%20pacer%20has%20brought%20his%20IPL%202024%20form%20into%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20continue%20being%20India's%20X-factor%20player%20as%20he%20looks%20to%20add%20to%20his%2079%20scalps%20on%20the%20T20I%20stage%20against%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft-arm%20pacer%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20also%20had%20a%20notable%20IPL%202024%20campaign%20and%20the%20fast%20bowler%20has%20replicated%20similar%20form%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%20by%20providing%20early%20breakthroughs%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20economy%20of%206.25%20to%20boast%2C%20Arshdeep%20has%20taken%20seven%20wickets%20in%20the%20tournament%20for%20India.%20He%20recorded%20his%20best%20bowling%20figures%20in%20T20Is%20against%20the%20USA%20in%20India's%20previous%20game%20with%20figures%20of%204%2F9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj%20showcased%20good%20form%20in%20India's%20opening%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20encounter%20by%20taking%20one%20wicket%20with%20a%20superb%20economy%20rate%20of%204.3%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20ability%20to%20swing%20the%20ball%20and%20provide%20breakthroughs%20in%20powerplay%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20advantage%20for%20India%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Siraj%20currently%20has%2013%20wickets%20in%20as%20many%20T20Is%20and%20he%20wil