ion%20is%20one%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20presenting%20his%20side%20of%20the%20case%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20impassioned%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20addressed%20the%20court%20directly%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20of%20trying%20%26quot%3Bto%20crush%26quot%3B%20his%20party.%20He%20pointed%20out%20-%20as%20the%20AAP%20had%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20do%20so%20-%20that%20no%20'bribes'%20allegedly%20received%20by%20his%20party%20had%20been%20recovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20arrested...%20but%20no%20court%20has%20proved%20me%20guilty.%20The%20CBI%2C%20or%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20filed%2031%2C000%20pages%20(of%20chargesheets)%20and%20ED%20filed%2025%2C000.%20Even%20if%20you%20read%20them%20together%20the%20question%20remains...%20why%20have%20I%20been%20arrested%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20statements%20of%20approvers%2C%20or%20accused%20individuals%20who%20became%20government%20witnesses%2C%20suggesting%20they%20had%20been%20coerced%20into%20accusing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmany-come-to-my-house-is-this-enough-to-arrest-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-5326460%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BProbe%20Agency's%202%20Missions%3A%20Finish%20AAP%20And...%26quot%3B%3A%20Kejriwal%20In%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ED%20had%20only%20one%20mission%20-%20to%20trap%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3BThree%20statements%20were%20given%20(by%20one%20witness)...%20but%20the%20court%20only%20saw%20those%20that%20accused%20me.%20Why%3F%20This%20is%20not%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20March%2021%2C%20on%20charges%20he%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20setting%2