p%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20several%20remote%20workers%20were%20fired%20after%20allegedly%20simulating%20keyboard%20activity%20to%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20were%20actively%20working%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWells%20Fargo%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20it%20has%20strict%20standards%20and%20won't%20%E2%80%9Ctolerate%20unethical%20behaviour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20mouse%20jigglers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMouse%20jigglers%20are%20small%20devices%20or%20software%20programs%20designed%20to%20prevent%20a%20computer%20from%20going%20into%20sleep%20mode%20or%20activating%20its%20screensaver%20due%20to%20inactivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThey%20work%20by%20simulating%20small%2C%20automatic%20and%20random%20movements%20of%20the%20mouse%20cursor%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20fooling%20the%20computer%20into%20thinking%20that%20there%20is%20user%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20detect%20if%20someone%20is%20using%20mouse%20jigglers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECheck%20for%20software%20and%20devices%20on%20company%20computers%20for%20any%20unauthorised%20apps%20that%20could%20be%20mouse%20jigglers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EObserve%20employee%20responsiveness%20during%20work%20hours.%20Mouse%20jigglers%20cannot%20mimic%20human%20interaction%20like%20responding%20to%20messages%20or%20participating%20in%20calls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EImplement%20certain%20apps%20and%20softwares%20to%20track%20mouse%20movements%20and%20activity.%20These%20tools%20will%20detect%20abnormal%20patterns%20that%20could%20signify%20the%20use%20of%20mouse%20jigglers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEducate%20employees%20on%20the%20risks%20of%20using%20mouse%20jigglers%20and%20implement%20policies%20against%20their%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20people%20use%20mouse%20jigglers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEmployees%20use%20mouse%20jigglers%20when%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20computers%20active%20during%20short%20breaks%20or%20interruptions%2C%20like%20bathroom%20visits%20or%20childcare%20duties%20while%20working%20remotely.%20This%20prevents%20the%20computer%20from%20showing%20them%20as%20inactive%20or%20entering%20sleep%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20also%20comes%20in%20handy%20when%20they%20need%20uninterrupted%20time%20to%20read%20documents%20or%20complete%20tasks%20that%20require%20constant%20access%20to%20the%20file%20but%20they%20do%20not%20want%20their%20screen%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%20mode%20while%20they%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718431260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm4ae21dg_computer_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwells-fargo-fires-employees-over-mouse-jiggling-heres-what-it-means-5894560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mouse%20jigglers%20are%20software%20programs%20that%20automatically%20move%20the%20mouse%20cursor%20slightly%20and%20randomly%20to%20prevent%20a%20computer%20from%20going%20into%20sleep%20mode%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwells-fargo-fires-employees-over-mouse-jiggling-heres-what-it-means-5894560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shakib%20On%20Rift%20With%20Tamim%3A%20BCB%20Chief's%20Comments%20%26quot%3BCreated%20This%20Situation%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20star%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F792-shakib-al-hasan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShakib%20Al%20Hasan%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20that%20Bangladesh%20Cricket%20Board%20(BCB)%20Nazmul%20Hasan's%20comment%20ignited%20the%20rift%20between%20himself%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tamim%20Iqbal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F902-tamim-iqbal-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETamim%20Iqbal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20national%20team's%20two%20senior%20cricket%20players%20were%20reportedly%20at%20odds%20with%20each%20other%2C%20according%20to%20the%20BCB%20chief.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20that%20revelation%20about%20the%20two%20veterans%20became%20a%20hot%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20Bangladeshi%20cricket.%20In%20a%20documentary%20aired%20by%20Bongo%2C%20a%20leading%20OTT%20platform%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20Shakib%20addressed%20the%20controversy%2C%20revealing%20how%20Hasan's%20remarks%20created%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20thing%20came%20to%20focus%20after%20Papon%20(Nazmul%20Hasan)%20Bhai%20spoke%20about%20it%20and%20it%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%20on%20the%20relationship%20and%20created%20this%20situation.%20I%20think%20some%20people%20had%20the%20intention%20to%20keep%20it%20(the%20rift)%20in%20focus%20and%20tried%20to%20make%20it%20as%20the%20main%20point%20(of%20discussion)%20rather%20than%20the%20cricketing%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Also%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fazam-khan-wont-return-to-pakistan-because-t20-world-cup-exit-sets-internet-ablaze-5894010%5C%22%3E'Azam%20Khan%20Won't%20Return%20To%20Pakistan%20Because...'%3A%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Exit%20Sets%20Internet%20Ablaze%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamim%20has%20been%20inconsistent%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20squad%20after%20the%20back%20injury%2C%20he%20was%20out%20of%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20and%20was%20also%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20World%20Cup%20squad%2C%20citing%20a%20persistent%20back%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Tamim%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20Facebook%2C%20claiming%20he%20was%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20squad%20due%20to%20growing%20tension%20between%20him%20and%20BCB%20officials%20instead%20of%20not%20being%20fit%20enough%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20a%20documentary%2C%20while%20Tamim%20downplayed%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20relationship%20on%20the%20team%2C%20Shakib%20had%20a%20different%20perspective.%20%26quot%3BFor%20quite%20some%20time%20we%20were%20not%20talking%20a%20lot.%20%5BBut%5D%20it%20is%20not%20right%20that%20we%20were%20not%20on%20talking%20terms.%20The%20thing%20is%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20used%20to%20be%20together%20all%20the%20time%20but%20that%20relationship%20was%20not%20there%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20the%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20natural...%20I%20got%20married%20and%20he%20got%20married%2C%20we%20were%20staying%20separately%20in%20different%20places%20and%20so%20there%20was%20very%20lesser%20time%20between%20us.%20We%20were%20staying%20in%20the%20same%20building%20in%20different%20floors%20%5Bearlier%5D%20so%20certainly%20that%20closeness%20starts%20to%20diminish%20as%20people%20start%20having%20separate%20family%20life%20and%20over%20time%20(the%20relationship)%20changed%20due%20to%20our%20busy%20schedules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakib%20emphasised%20that%20despite%20the%20distance%2C%20their%20professional%20relationship%20remained%20intact.%20%26quot%3BLater%20what%20happened%20is%20that%20in%20the%20field%20when%20we%20met%2C%20we%20have%20spoken%20whenever%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20need%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20between%20us%20apart%20from%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Read%20More%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshoaib-akhtars-one-line-post-goes-viral-after-pakistans-exit-from-t20-world-cup-5893922%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar's%20One%20Line%20Post%20Goes%20Viral%20After%20Pakistan's%20Exit%20From%20T20%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20underscored%20that%20their%20interactions%20were%20sufficient%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20team%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20extra%20efforts%20to%20bridge%20any%20perceived%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20making%20it%20good%20or%20bad%20(as%20far%20as%20the%20relationship%20with%20Tamim%20is%20concerned).%20Till%20we%20played%20together%20and%20shared%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20incident%20took%20place%20that%20would%20harm%20the%20team.%20We%20tried%20to%20contribute%20whether%20we%20were%20talking%20or%20not%3B%20there%20was%20no%20kind%20of%20problem%20inside%20the%20field%20or%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20particularly%20controversial%20interview%20ahead%20of%20last%20year's%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20he%20accused%20Tamim%20of%20being%20irresponsible%2C%20Shakib%20clarified%20his%20intentions.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20try%20to%20give%20any%20message%20through%20that%20interview%20as%20it%20was%20certainly%20spontaneous.%20I%20felt%20that%20before%20going%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20I%20should%20clear%20everything%20so%20that%20people%20know%20what%20actually%20happened%20and%20why%20this%20kind%20of%20situation%20is%20created%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20st