C%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20install%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20terrace%20of%20your%20apartment%20complex%20and%20the%20society%20cannot%20refuse%20the%20request%2C%20provided%20there%20is%20a%20vacant%20space%20available%20on%20the%20rooftop.%20You%20can%20move%20the%20court%20if%20the%20society%20denies%20your%20request.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kiran%20suggests%20conducting%20shadow%20analysis%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352174%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKiran%20suggests%20conducting%20shadow%20analysis%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20if%20you%20live%20on%2C%20say%2C%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%2020-storey%20building%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20bringing%20the%20cable%20(wire)%20down%20from%20the%20terrace%20would%20be%20enormous.%20The%20add-ons%20could%20run%20into%20an%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2211%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20you%20can%20opt%20for%20balconies%20which%20can%20minimise%20the%20cabling%20cost%20as%20the%20whole%20system%20would%20be%20drawn%20to%20your%20house%20including%20the%20net%20metre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20viable%20proposition%20for%20apartment%20owners%20and%20tenants%20with%20rental%20agreements%20for%2010%20or%2015%20years.%20Tenants%20cannot%20remove%20the%20setup%20to%20take%20it%20somewhere%20else%20because%20it%20will%20again%20involve%20paperwork%20and%20installation%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2212%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20assume%20the%20monthly%20power%20expenses%20to%20be%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20installation%20and%20inverter%20(with%20a%2010-year%20warranty)%20to%20be%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20So%2C%20for%20a%2015-year%20contract%2C%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20will%20be%20generated%20only%20after%20five%20years%20and%20residents%20can%20avail%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20free%20electricity%20provided%20the%20inverter%20lasts%20for%20say%2013%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20landlord%20will%20incur%20the%20capital%20cost%20for%20the%20new%20inverter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Using%20balconies%20could%20not%20be%20very%20feasible%20if%20the%20energy%20generation%20will%20be%20small-scale%20compared%20to%20the%20requirement.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20safety%20risks%20from%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20lightning%20strikes%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20cyclones%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKiran%20points%20out%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20involved%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20boards.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20contract%20term%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20provider%20and%20the%20subsidy.%20The%20service%20provider%20and%20the%20solar%20installation%20companies%20will%20help%20do%20the%20paperwork%20but%20ensure%20that%20you%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2215%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20further%20asks%20residents%20to%20consider%20the%20maths%20on%20subsequent%20savings.%20If%20your%20monthly%20power%20bill%20is%20Rs%202%2C500%20in%20a%202BHK%2C%20then%20you%20will%20recover%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20installation%20in%2010%20years%20(assuming%20rooftop%20cable%20wiring%20expenses%20in%20addition%20to%20inverter%20and%20installation%20costs%20totaling%20Rs%203%20lakh).%20It%20does%20not%20make%20sense%20if%20the%20monthly%20bill%20is%20Rs%201%2C000-1%2C200%20and%20tenants%20move%20out%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Photo%20credit%3A%20Adobe%20stock%20images%2C%20Bhoomi%20Arkade%2C%20and%20Palash%20Co-Operative%20Housing%20Society)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717591462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1717589888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352016%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Want%20to%20harness%20solar%20energy%20in%20your%20apartment%20and%20save%20on%20monthly%20electricity%20bills%3F%20Experts%20share%2015%20factors%20to%20consider%20for%20solar%20panel%20installation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%