Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Mandeep%20Verma%E2%80%99s%20farming%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandeep%20Verma%20left%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%20Delhi%20to%20start%20Swaastik%20Farms%2C%20an%20organic%20fruit%20farm%20in%20Shilli%20village%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%205-acre%20farm%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20foothills%2C%20produces%20kiwis%20and%20apples%20without%20using%20any%20chemicals%2C%20and%20yields%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20prior%20farming%20experience%2C%20he%20learned%20through%20online%20resources%20and%20consultations%20with%20local%20agricultural%20experts%2C%20transforming%20his%20barren%2C%20sloped%20land%20which%20took%20five%20months.%20He%20planted%20150%20kiwi%20plants%2C%20using%20organic%20methods%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrut%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esapta%20dhanyankur%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20soil%20nutrition%2C%20and%20later%20added%201%2C200%20apple%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20his%20farm%20now%20has%20700%20kiwi%20plants%20yielding%209%20tonnes%20of%20fruit%20annually%2C%20with%20expected%20production%20increases.%20He%20also%20developed%20two%20nurseries%20with%2012%2C000%20saplings%20for%20additional%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swaastik%20farms'%20organic%20kiwi.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FKiwi-farm1-1647262025-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-279013%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKiwis%20at%20Mandeep%E2%80%99s%20farm.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Mandeep%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Rohan%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20certified%20mangoes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family%20watching%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%2C%20Rohan%20Prakash%20felt%20an%20affinity%20for%20fields%20and%20farms.%20The%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20agriculture%20led%20him%20to%20convert%20their%20farm%20into%20a%20completely%20organic%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20to%20organic%20farming%20yielded%20immediate%20improvements%20in%20the%20quality%20and%20size%20of%20their%20mangoes.%20The%20transformation%20process%20started%20during%20his%20second%20year%20of%20college%20when%20he%20and%20his%20father%20decided%20to%20replace%20pesticides%20with%20Neem%20oil%20extract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20results%2C%20Rohan%20branded%20their%20produce%20as%20%E2%80%9CSure%20Organics%E2%80%9D.%20Rohan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20grows%20various%20mango%20varieties%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3Edasheri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Elangra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Echaunsa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Esafeda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20along%20with%20lychee%20and%20turmeric.%20Over%20three%20years%2C%20his%20farm%20achieved%20organic%20certification%2C%20boosting%20their%20revenue%20significantly%20and%20increasing%20overall%20productivity%20by%2040%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20S%20Sivaganesh%E2%80%99s%20homecoming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20an%20atomic%20station%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20S%20Sivaganesh%20a